Workout: Functional Endurance Circuit (≈45 min | Fokus: Ausdauer, Functional)

Warm-Up | 5 min | Mobilität & Cardio
- Jumping Jacks  
    - 60 s | –  
- Leg Swings Front-to-Back  
    - 10 reps (je Seite) | –  
- Leg Swings Side-to-Side  
    - 10 reps (je Seite) | –  
- World’s Greatest Stretch  
    - 5 reps (je Seite) | –  

Main | 35 min | 3 Runden Circuit, P: 60 s zwischen Stationen
- AirBike 50 cal  
    - 50 cal / P: 60 s | –  
    - 50 cal / P: 60 s | –  
    - 50 cal / P: 60 s | –  
- Sled Push Heavy  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
- Sled Pull Heavy  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m / P: 60 s | –  
- Farmer’s Carry (Dumbbell)  
    - 20 m @ 24 kg / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m @ 24 kg / P: 60 s | –  
    - 20 m @ 24 kg / P: 60 s | –  
- Wall Ball Shot  
    - 15 @ 9 kg / P: 60 s | –  
    - 15 @ 9 kg / P: 60 s | –  
    - 15 @ 9 kg / P: 60 s | –  
- Burpee Broad Jump  
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –  
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –  
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –  

Cool-Down | 5 min | Stretching & Mobility
- Pigeon Pose (Reclined)  
    - 45 s / P: 15 s | –  
- Downward Dog to Cobra  
    - 60 s / P: 15 s | –  
- Cat-Cow Flow  
    - 60 s / P: 15 s | –
